    Class Description
    AuthenticatedEvent
    Event fired when the authentication has succeded or failed
    ConnectedEvent
    Event fired when the initialization process has succeded or failed

    GlobalEvent
    Base class for all Rtcc global events.
    GlobalResultEvent<T extends Error>
    Base class for events that can fail.

    This event is fired in response to a RtccEngine.getStatus(String) request.
